creator: Studio 117
descriptionHtml:
Standupr is the go-to app for stand-up comedians, making it easier than ever to organize bits, manage setlists, and record your shows.

Standupr helps bring your comedy into the 21st century by making it easier than ever to manage all of your bits, sets, and shows in one easy place. Share them with friends to get feedback, and keep your writing with you wherever you go.

Whether you're an open mic'er just getting going, or you're an established comedian with a solid following, Standupr gives you the tools you need to really improve on your comedy and take it to the next level.

- Track bits & organize by color coding
- Prepare sets with your bits
- Track the estimated length of your sets
- Track your shows & record your sets in one central spot
- Organize your setlist for each show
- Listen to your recorded sets so you can see where you did well and where you can improve

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added media playback controls for show recordings
- Fixed bugs with organizing bits in set lists
- Minor UI improvements
